  <entry>
    <title>Vagrant-scp - copy files to vagrant VMs easily</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://blog.url.com/blog/2015/01/26/vagrant-scp-copy-files-to-vagrant-vms/"/>
    <id>http://blog.url.com/blog/2015/01/26/vagrant-scp-copy-files-to-vagrant-vms/</id>
    <published>2015-01-26T15:10:00-08:00</published>
    <updated>2015-01-26T15:19:20-08:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Article Author</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;I faced quite a few times the problem of copying files to virtual machines started via &lt;a href="https://www.vagrantup.com/"&gt;Vagrant&lt;/a&gt;.
Since &lt;a href="http://minimul.com/ssh-and-scp-into-a-vagrant-box.html"&gt;many&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24941237/unable-to-scp-files-from-local-machine-into-vagrant"&gt;people&lt;/a&gt; were facing the same issue, I&amp;rsquo;ve written a quick  Vagrant plugin to solve this problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Install it via:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="highlight shell"&gt;vagrant plugin install vagrant-scp
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use it like so:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="highlight shell"&gt;vagrant scp &amp;lt;some_local_file_or_dir&amp;gt; &amp;lt;somewhere_on_the_vm&amp;gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;vm_name]
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
